    <measure>Patient pain level follow pterygium removal</measure>
    <time_frame>2 months</time_frame>
    <description>measurement of pain following pterygium removal using the validated &quot;Numeric Pain Rating Scale&quot; to assess pain, which ranges from 0 to 10 with higher values indicating more severe pain.</description>
